data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom 2.5 bath open floorplan townhome built in 2019 located in Tapestry in Kissimmee Florida. The Tapestry is located close to all major highways, shopping, restaurants and theme parks. The home has brand new interior paint throughout. Your new home has a rear entry 2 car garage. All of your bedrooms are located upstairs for your privacy and convenience. Outside of your master bedroom you have a spacious balcony great for relaxing after a long days of work. Your master bathroom has dual sinks and a walkin shower. Your kitchen has granite countertops with backsplash, ss appliances and lots of recess lights. Your stairs have carpet and bathrooms have tile flooring while the remaining areas of the home have luxury vinyl flooring. Schedule your showing today.
